name: Over the Moon (dagworth)
description:
Where a slime saves the world by stealing the moon.

You use your mouse to jump. Remember that you can double jump!

There are only 10 levels.

First game jam I participated in! (Mini Jam 130: Lunar)

My high score was 36.21 seconds, try to beat it! (I tried for like an hour lol)
